high_descs: Turn right and go forward, turn right and head to the counter where the bread is.
Pick up the yellow handled knife that is on the counter.
Turn right, go to the counter, turn right, go to the counter across the room where the tomato is.
Use the knife to cut the tomato into slices.
Turn around and head to the wall, hang a left and head to the microwave across the room.
Put the knife inside the microwave.
Turn around and go forward, turn right and head to the counter where the tomato is.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the counter.
Turn around and head to the wall, hang a left and head to the microwave across the room.
Put the tomato inside the microwave and turn it on to cook, remove the tomato when it is done cooking.
Turn around, go forward, hang a left and go to the sink.
Put the tomato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put hot tomato in a sink.

high_descs: Turn and go to the counter to the left of the sink where the bread is on the counter.
Pick up the knife that is on the counter.
Turn around and go to the counter behind you where the tomato is with the knife.
Slice the tomato with the knife.
With the knife in hand turn and go to the microwave.
Open the microwave and place the knife in there. Close the door.
Turn and go to the tomato you sliced.
Pick up a slice of tomato that is on the right side.
With the tomato slice in hand turn and go to the microwave.
Open the microwave. Place the tomato slice in the microwave behind the knife. Close the door and start the microwave.  When finished take out the tomato slice and close the door.
With the tomato slice in hand go to the sink.
Place the tomato slice in the sink in the right front corner.
anns.task_desc: Warm up tomato slice and knife to put tomato in sink.

high_descs: Turn around and head toward the bread on the counter.
Pick up the knife next to the bread on the counter.
Turn around and head toward the tomato on the counter.
Slice the tomato with the knife.
Turn right and head toward the microwave above the stove.
Open the microwave and put the knife inside the microwave.
Turn around, go forward toward the wall, then turn right toward the sliced tomato on the counter
Pick up a slice of tomato from the counter
Turn right and head toward the microwave above the stove.
Put the tomato slice next to the knife in the microwave, microwave them both, and then take the tomato slice out of the microwave
Turn to the right and head toward the sink.
Put the tomato slice into the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved tomato slice into the sink.
